---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about Rohith Saripalli, a Senior Software Engineer"
>
  <main id="main">
    <div class="about__content" transition:animate="fade">
      <section class="section">
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <p>
          I'm a Senior Software Engineer with 5+ years of experience building
          scalable full-stack systems and tackling complex engineering
          challenges. I work across frontend and backend with TypeScript, React,
          .NET (C#), TiDB, and AWS, with a strong focus on performance,
          distributed systems, and cloud-native architecture.
        </p>
        <p>
          Currently <strong>Conga</strong>, I contribute across the stack to
          build reliable, scalable solutions, while deepening my interest in
          AI-driven problem solving and modern distributed systems design. I
          enjoy working on hard technical problems, adapting quickly to new
          technologies, and building software that delivers both technical
          excellence and real user value.
        </p>

        <div class="resume-cta">
          <a
            href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1c992oQjdFieYtfLahD_pC78odY9_2YHe/view?usp=sharing"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="btn btn--primary"
            aria-label="Download Rohith's resume (PDF, opens in new tab)"
            transition:animate="fade"
          >
            📄 Download Resume
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Skills & Technologies</h2>
        <div class="skills-grid">
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h3>Frontend</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Next.js</li>
              <li>React</li>
              <li>Redux</li>
              <li>TypeScript</li>
              <li>JavaScript (ES6+)</li>
              <li>CSS3 & SCSS</li>
              <li>Web Performance</li>
              <li>Accessibility (WCAG)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h3>Backend, DB & Infrastructure</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>.Net Core</li>
              <li>C#</li>
              <li>Node.js</li>
              <li>TiDB</li>
              <li>RESTful APIs</li>
              <li>Database Design (SQL / NoSQL)</li>
              <li>System Design & Architecture</li>
              <li>Cloud Services (AWS / Azure)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h3>Tools & Practices</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Git & GitHub</li>
              <li>CI/CD Pipelines</li>
              <li>Testing (Jest, RTL, E2E)</li>
              <li>Agile / Scrum</li>
              <li>Technical Leadership</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Interests & Focus Areas</h2>
        <ul class="interests-list">
          <li>🤖 AI & Machine Learning Applications</li>
          <li>🔄 Distributed Systems & Scalability</li>
          <li>⚡ Web Performance Optimization</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about__content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .section h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-category {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .skill-category ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .skill-category li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-category li::before {
    content: '▸';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-hover);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .interests-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .interests-list li {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about__content {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .section h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .skills-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .resume-cta {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .resume-cta .btn {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 2.5rem;
  }
</style>
